node.title: Two critical after workers overcome by fumes cleaning tank in Auckland - report
node.description: Police say it appears one person was cleaning the tank and the others may have gone to their assistance.
node.content: ["Emergency services are responding to reports three people have been affected by carbon monoxide fumes while cleaning a tank in Kumeu, Auckland.", "Police say they were informed at about 8:30pm on Monday.\u00a0", "\"It appears one person was cleaning the tank and the others may have gone to their assistance,\" a police spokesperson says.", "\"Two of the three are reported to be in a critical condition. More details will be available as they come to hand.\""]
